# {{app_name}} Backend

The backend is built with FastAPI and Uvicorn.

## Setting Up the Development Environment (Python)
- **Environment Manager**:
  - [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/)
  - [PDM](https://pdm.fming.dev/)
- **Linter**:
  - [Ruff](https://github.com/astral-sh/ruff)
- **Test Framework**:
  - [Pytest](https://docs.pytest.org/en/latest/)

**Steps**:
1. Install **uv**:
   ```bash
   brew install uv
   ```

or install **PDM**:
   ```bash
   pipx install pdm
   # or
   pip install pdm
   # or
   brew install pdm
   ```

2. Initialize the project:
   ```bash
   cd backend
   uv sync
   # or
   pdm install
   ```

3. Run the backend:
   ```bash
   cd backend
   fastapi dev app/main.py
   # or
   pdm run uvicorn app.main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000
   ```

